OL,3,CCouncil fined after man falls while
OL,4,Cinstalling town's Christmas tree
OL,6,FThe 32-year-old operations manager
OL,7,Fsuffered concussion and severe
OL,8,Finjuries to his right-hand side,
OL,9,Fincluding bruising to his ribs.
OL,11,FHe needed an operation to his leg and
OL,12,Fwas left using a wheelchair and
OL,13,Fcrutches after sustaining a large cut
OL,14,Fto his leg.
OL,16,FMr Lyth was off work for two months
OL,17,Fand was subsequently only able to
OL,18,Freturn on restricted hours and duties
OL,19,Fas he continued his recovery.
