OL,3,CCouncil fined after man falls while
OL,4,Cinstalling town's Christmas tree
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that Bury
OL,8,FMetropolitan Borough Council had
OL,9,Ffailed to provide Mr Lyth with any
OL,10,Ftraining in the safe operation of the
OL,11,Fscissor lift and had failed carry out
OL,12,Fa sufficient risk assessment for this
OL,13,Fwork activity.
OL,15,FThe investigation also found that a
OL,16,Fsuitable risk assessment of the work
OL,17,Fwould have identified the dangers
OL,18,Finvolved and the need to restrict the
OL,19,Fuse of scissor lifts to those with
OL,20,Fappropriate training.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
