OL,3,CCouncil fined after man falls while
OL,4,Cinstalling town's Christmas tree
OL,6,FBury Council pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fbreaching the Health and Safety at
OL,8,FWork Act and was fined #200,000 and
OL,9,Fordered to pay costs.
OL,11,FHSE inspector Leanne Ratcliffe said:
OL,12,F"This was a very serious incident.
OL,14,F"It is important for industry to
OL,15,Funderstand the importance of a risk
OL,16,Fassessment and training when using
OL,17,Felevated platforms.
