OL,3,CCouncil fined after man falls while
OL,4,Cinstalling town's Christmas tree
OL,6,F"Access to these platforms should be
OL,7,Flimited to those trained and anyone
OL,8,Fwho isn't trained shouldn't be allowed
OL,9,Fto use them.
OL,11,F"If this sort of work is not planned
OL,12,Fand controlled to a high degree, then
OL,13,Fthere is a very high likelihood of a
OL,14,Fpotentially fatal fall, or one
OL,15,Fresulting in very serious injury."
